channel.description: Resources Slides Video Script Hello and welcome to the week 15 announcements video for CIS 527 and CC 510 in fall 2024. So all that’s really remaining in this class is lab 7 and the final project both of which are due on the Friday of finals week so you’ve got a little bit over a week and a half to work on those. We’ll also have teaching evaluations at the end of the semester so let’s talk about all of that.
